# Launcher line endings. The repo is developed on Windows (core.autocrlf=true),
# which would otherwise check .sh out with CRLF — a CRLF shebang/`exec` line
# breaks the bash launchers on Linux/macOS. Pin them to LF; pin .ps1 to CRLF for
# native Windows editing (PowerShell accepts either). Scoped to scripts only so
# the rest of the tree keeps its existing, working behaviour.
*.sh  text eol=lf
*.ps1 text eol=crlf
